      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/68/1394",
      "text": [
        " طَلَبِ اَلرِّزْقِ وَ حَذَرَهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1394 - Imam (as) said:\n\"Learn three qualities from the crow: its concealment when mating, its early rising in seeking sustenance, and its cautiousness.\""
        ]
      }
